<p>John and Dave are busy again this week, answering your questions about Time Machine drives, Safari&rsquo;s Activity window, a wonky screen saver, and why several listeners&rsquo; Macs might be freezing. A comment from a listener about Apple upgrading a MacBook Pro to 6GB when 4GB is the officially supported configuration is included, as well as a host of other topics. Download (it&rsquo;s free!) and enjoy!</p>
